snippet.title: Animated Story Trailer - Legends of Equestria Open Access Release
snippet.description:
Legends of Equestria now available for download: https://forum.legendsofequestria.com/index.php?topic=16775

Experience the story of Legends of Equestria! Adventure through Equestria with a colourful (literally) cast of characters; grow alongside them, and work together to make Equestria a better world!

Legends of Equestria is an in-development family-friendly MMORPG set in the world of Equestria, developed by an all-volunteer team over five years.

Animated by our team member Rika; check out her own animations on her channel here: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCoJ1dMFWL2V2wMdJdnKb2pw

Voices provided by members of our VA team - FirePetalFox, Burgundy Patches, Kenzie VA, Galapagois
